Unitron/Anubis/Hades:



Unitron and Anubis set the BHIC-Class Crate filled with 50 kilos of liquid 
energon to the ground softly.

Unitron tapped his chest, his comm. unit activating.  "This is Unitron, under 
Koga Shuko's command," he said, a comlink established witht he Ark, "I, and 
two others, have brought your crate of energon."

The three Newcomers awaited the response of their Maximal enemies.
